title: Azada Ancient Magic.exe
description:
The adventurer Titus has been magically bound to a mystical puzzle book by his evil great-uncle. To help free him from his prison, you must solve a series of mind-bending puzzles in the book of Azada.

Fill in the missing pages of the enchanted book through uncovering clues and codes to free Titus from his prison. Each page of the book has a new puzzle in store. Get ready to be kept on your toes!
